<HEADLINE>
MILLIONS SPENT TO IMPRESS THOUSANDS AT CONVENTION
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By BRENT HOPKINS 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR; LOS ANGELES _ In anticipation of the crush of national media
in town for the Democratic National Convention, Los Angeles has
received a multimillion-dollar face lift.
</P>
