<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-13 17:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0375 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-FLA-BEACH-ART-NYT &LR;      08-13 1193
