<HEADLINE>
SCHEDULE FOR DEMOCRATIC NATIONAL CONVENTION 
</HEADLINE>
   c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   (All times are Eastern daylight)
</P>
<P>
   8 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Tribute to firefighters and police officers.
</P>
