<P>
   The New York Times News Service is planning the following
convention coverage for editions of Monday, Aug. 14.
</P>
<P>
   All convention stories will be filed in the ``p'' category and
will carry a convention-designation prefix of DEM- in the slug;
e.g., BC-DEM-CONVENTION-NYT.
