   FOLD
</P>
<P>
   WELFARELESS-COUNTY (Rushville, Ill.) _ Welfare has completely
disappeared from Schuyler County, Ill. For more than a year, there
have been no new cases, no old cases, no one on the rolls. This
results not just from a strong economy, but also from hard work by
local welfare officials, who give lots of personal attention to
each case _ and have many lessons to teach the rest of the country.
By Robert Pear.
</P>
