<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-13 21:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0492 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u p BC-CVN-CONVENTION-RDP-HN     08-13 1261
